extends site-layout

block head
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/about-custom.css")

block content
    //- The site-layout already has the base typography and structure.
    
    section.hero
        h1 About Dracarys
        p We believe every child deserves access to an inspiring, affordable, and safe learning experience — no matter their background or budget.
        
    //- REMOVED the extra 'main' tag from here so CSS grids can work properly
    section.mission
        h2 Our Mission
        p Dracarys is a community-driven tuition marketplace built by university students, for school students. We connect enthusiastic university students and subject experts with primary and secondary school pupils, bridging the gap between academic levels through peer-to-peer learning. Our platform makes education more <strong>accessible</strong>, more <strong>affordable</strong>, and genuinely more <strong>fun</strong>.
        
    section.stats
        .stat-box
            .num 10+
            .label Verified Tutors
        .stat-box
            .num 10
            .label Subjects Available
        .stat-box
            .num 100%
            .label Safety Verified
            
    section.team
        h2 Meet the Team
        .team-grid
            .member
                .avatar(style="background:var(--primary)") SK
                h4 Suprem Karki
                p.student-id A00020626
                p.role Backend & DevOps
            .member
                .avatar(style="background:var(--secondary)") RS
                h4 Raja Shah
                p.student-id A00020547
                p.role Frontend & Design
            .member
                .avatar(style="background:var(--success)") SS
                h4 Sadun Sudu Dewage
                p.student-id A00019034
                p.role Database & Docs
            .member
                .avatar(style="background:var(--gold)") AL
                h4 Aman Lamjel
                p.student-id A00016965
                p.role Testing & Ethics
                
    section.values
        h2 Our Core Values
        .values-grid
            .value-card
                h4 Accessibility
                p Quality education should not be limited by financial barriers. We offer affordable community-based tutoring for all families.
            .value-card
                h4 Child Safety
                p Every tutee is a minor. We verify all tutors, provide parental oversight tools, and monitor all communications for safety.
            .value-card
                h4 Engagement
                p Learning should be exciting. Our tutors use interactive methods, games, and real-life examples to make subjects come alive.
            .value-card
                h4 Community
                p We believe in sharing knowledge cooperatively, for mutual benefit. Dracarys is built on the principle of giving back.
            .value-card
                h4 Fairness
                p Transparent pricing, fair treatment of tutors, and equal access regardless of background, gender, or learning needs.
            .value-card
                h4 Growth
                p We track and celebrate progress. Every session note, every review, and every badge represents a step forward.
                
    section.ethics
        h2 Our Commitment to Safety & Ethics
        p Dracarys was designed with child safeguarding at its core. All tutors are verified with university email addresses. Parents have full visibility over all messaging between tutors and their children. We comply fully with GDPR — collecting only the minimum data required. Our platform includes a content flagging system, moderation controls, and a clear code of conduct for all tutors. We are committed to inclusivity, accessibility (WCAG 2.1 AA), and bias-free matching.
        
    section.about-cta
        h2 Ready to Join the Community?
        p Whether you're a parent looking for a tutor, or a university student wanting to give back — Dracarys is for you.
        //- Updated the href to point to your actual signup route
        a.btn(href="/signup") Get Started Today